{"id": "1366391258733477898", "channel_id": "1366391258733477898", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人你好：\n       彌薩格大學校務處將於4月28日 21:15 進行校內設施修復，更新完成後您將得到通知，重新進入遊戲。對於更新可能給大家帶來的不便，我們會準備一份補給物資以示歉意。祝大家調查順利！ \n  \n【補給物資】\n在線維護補償：銀芯*50\n  \n【領取條件】\n領取時間截至2025年5月12日23:59。請記得及時前往郵箱領取補給物資哦。  \n \n【更新內容】\n● 修復了融災地圖節點錯誤為「融痕」和「聯絡點」的問題。\n● 修復了在「忘卻篇」關卡中命輪「湧現」融痕刷新費用降低效果未正確生效的問題。\n● 修復了衍生卡「領航」當喚醒體「克珀珊特」不在隊伍中時，數值為 0 的問題。\n● 修復了「克萊門汀 · 維度影像」在探索中有概率重複出現的問題。\n● 修復了造物預覽列表中出現了重複造物問題。\n● 修復了喚醒體「卡茜亞」的技能「隔空取物」取出帶有「超距」詞綴的卡牌時，未能使其正確降低算力消耗的問題。\n● 修復了喚醒體「墨菲」釋放狂氣爆發「虛妄繼承者」後，若期間進入了超維回合，承受主動傷害時候不會被正確施加「獻祭」的問題。\n● 修復了活動紅點殘留的問題。\n● 修復了相位對弈中，傷害轉回復類效果失效的問題。   \n● 修復了相位對弈中，「達芙黛爾」的狂氣爆發給予其他友方狂氣的效果失效的問題。\n● 「黃金週特別活動：掃除奇旅」中「今日掃除完成！」的任務完成條件調整為：任意完成3個每日掃除任務。今日已完成部分任務的守密人可以通過重新登入遊戲刷新完成進度。\n● 修復了卡牌標題超出框的表現問題。", "timestamp": "2025-04-28T12:31:02.404000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-04-28T13:14:21.165000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "idk", "emoji_id": "1356084138280489080", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1366391259656355951", "filename": "lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131424, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366391258733477898/1366391259656355951/lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg?ex=69cc6746&is=69cb15c6&hm=c805703b53a05645594ecb12203d2df245835b55c7d91c1b063707af869e76af&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366391258733477898", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.1.1 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1366391345081487463", "channel_id": "1366391258733477898", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "V2.2.1.1 Online Maintenance Notice\nDear Keeper,\n    The Mythag University Administration Office will conduct facility repairs on April 28 at 21:15(UTC+8). You will be notified once the update is complete and can re-enter the game. We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause and will provide a supply package as compensation. Happy investigating!\n    \n【Supply Package】\nMaintenance Compensation: Silver*50\n    \n【Claim Conditions】\nClaim period ends on May 12 2025(UTC+8), at 23:59. Please remember to check your mailbox to claim the supply package.\n     \n【Update Content】\n● Fixed the issue where disaster map nodes were incorrectly labeled as \"D-Mark\" and \"Junction.\"\n● Fixed the issue in the \"Forgotten Chapter\" stage where the Wheel of Destiny \"Emergence\" D-Mark refresh cost reduction effect was not applied correctly.\n● Fixed the issue with the derivative card \"Navigator\" where the value was 0 when the Awaker \"Corposant\" was not in the team.\n● Fixed the issue where \"Clementine · Dimensional Image\" could repeatedly appear during exploration.\n● Fixed the issue of duplicate relics appearing in the relic preview list.\n● Fixed the issue with the Awaker \"Casiah\" skill \"Remote Retrieval\" not correctly reducing Arithmetica consumption when extracting cards with the \"Transcend\" prefix.\n● Fixed the issue where the Awaker \"Murphy\" did not correctly apply \"Sacrifice\" when taking active damage after releasing the Aliemus Exaltation \"Heir to Delusion\" during an Ultra turn.\n● Fixed the issue of lingering activity notification dots.\n● Fixed the issue in Traphase where damage-to-heal effects were not working.\n● Fixed the issue in Traphase where \"Daffodil\" Aliemus Exaltation effect on other allies was not working.", "timestamp": "2025-04-28T12:31:22.991000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-04-29T07:17:43.138000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366391258733477898", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.1.1 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
